						<summary>

						<p>Stone found in the land survey No. 414 to the east of the village.</p>						

						<p>1483 A.D.</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka 1405, • • • śu. 15, Lunar eclipse.</p>						

						<p>Badly damaged and mutilated. It records the date portion and the people of Bukkapaṭnam.</p>						

